Megatron watches Autofire leave, aproving. Then he looks harshly at the
Quintesson, who scowls, and leaves. "I'll awnser that for you Scourge.
While I was trying to recharge, i found him buried under ice. I managed to
convince him to work for hire, for the Decepticons. But I dont like his
attitude, and dont trust him. Come, let's go see if Cyclonus has found out
the Maximal frequency, I wish to speak to their leader" he finishes,
smiling cruely. He walked out, waiting for Scourge to follow.


Sinnertwin got leapt on by Rippersnapper, and was being ground into the
earth. "Arggggg," snarl both of his heads, as one tries to bite
Rippersnapper. Speedbreaker looks on with a smile, then realises that
Astroblast is waiting for help, so he picks up some more metal. "Hun-grr,
where's Blot?" He asks.



Inside the base, the CR chambers holding the Stunticons chimes,
"Reparations almost complete". In the shadows the Quintesson slinks by, and
opens a small door, to small for most of the Decepticons to fit in. Inside
he closes the door. The room is light by computer screens. He rubs his
tentacles together, then moves towards the nearest screen.
